.DT
get_message
Disk World creator help
get_message

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
get_message -  Get the text of a specific message.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string get_message(string board,
int num,
string person)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^board%^RESET%^ - the board name to get the message from
%^BOLD%^num%^RESET%^ - the message number to use
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the message or 0 if it failed
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/board_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Get the text of a specific message.  This will look up the
text on a board with the given number and return that to the
caller.  The number is the offset into the subject array in
which to get the message from.
.EP

